OL,3,CDefence industry spend in NI up 20% in
OL,4,C2023
OL,6,FSpending by the Ministry of Defence
OL,7,F(MOD) in Northern Ireland has risen by
OL,8,F20% to #190m.
OL,10,FProcurement spend in the region rose
OL,11,Fby #31 million in 2023 to the highest
OL,12,Flevel in a decade.
OL,14,FThe majority of the increase relates
OL,15,Fto a major contract for Belfast-made
OL,16,Fanti-tank weapons used to support
OL,17,FUkraine's defence against Russia.
OL,19,FThe is manufactured in Belfast by
OL,20,FThales.
