OL,6,FThe supply of NLAW missiles makes up
OL,7,Fpart of the 10,000 anti-tank weapons
OL,8,Fthe United Kingdom has supplied to the
OL,9,FUkrainian armed forces.
OL,11,FThe #233 million four-year
OL,12,Fmanufacturing contract between the MOD
OL,13,Fand Thales was awarded in December
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FAn average of #100 is being spent on
OL,17,Fthe defence industry for each person
OL,18,Fliving in Northern Ireland.
