OL,4,C2023
OL,6,F600 jobs are supported through the
OL,7,FMOD's expenditure with the local
OL,8,Fdefence industry.
OL,10,FDefence Secretary, Grant Shapps said:
OL,11,F"As threats increase across the globe,
OL,12,Fit's crucial that investment in our
OL,13,FArmed Forces matches that picture.
OL,15,F"That's why we're spending more than
OL,16,F#50 billion annually on helping equip
OL,17,Four military with cutting-edge
OL,18,Fcapabilities, so they can continue to
OL,19,Fprotect our freedoms around the clock.
