OL,6,F"These statistics demonstrate how
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland is playing a key role
OL,8,Fin that crucial work, delivering
OL,9,Fthrough our fantastic defence industry
OL,10,Fand boosting local prosperity.
OL,12,F"The statistics highlight the
OL,13,Fgovernment's commitment to continually
OL,14,Fimproving the defence sector, while
OL,15,Fsupporting the economy and creating
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands of jobs across
OL,17,Fthe country.
OL,19,FDespite the increase, Northern Ireland
OL,20,Fis still the region of the UK with the
OL,21,Flowest defence procurement spending.
